high_descs: Move to the center of the tub.
Pick up the soap in the tub.
Turn around, bring the soap to the sink on the left.
Wash the soap in the left sink with water.
Take the wet soap in the sink, turn around and go to the trash can in the corner.
Put the wet soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in the trash can.

high_descs: Step back and move over to your right so that you are in front of the head of the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap, to the left of the purple rag, in the bath tub.
Turn around and go to the wall across the room, then turn to the sink to the right of you.
Place the bar of soap in the sink, turn the water on, get the bar of soap wet, turn the water off, and remove the bar of soap from the sink.
Turn around and go to the bucket of cleaning supplies, in the right corner of the room.
Place the bar of soap in the right side of the bucket.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the cleaning bucket.

high_descs: move to the tub ahead of you
pick up soap from the tub
move to the sink behind you
wet the soap in the sink
move to the bin behind you
put the soap in the bin
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the bin.
